DataSource.ConnectionString: Provider=SQLOLEDB.1;Password=sa;Persist Security Info=True;User ID=sa;Initial Catalog=mapacc;Data Source=ngannt
DataSource.RecordSource:
Declare @FromDate DateTime, @ToDate datetime
SET @FromDate = '2006-06-01 00:00:00' SET @ToDate = '2006-07-06 23:59:59'
SELECT a.MasLocCode, a.LocationID, a.LocationCode, a.BinCode, a.ProductID, a.PostDate, a.PartNumber, a.PartName, a.PartModel, a.UMCode, a.TransactionNo, a.TranTypeID, a.TranTypeName, a.BeginStock, a.BeginItemCost, a.StockItemCost, a.ItemCost, a.RelatedLocation, a.RelatedBin,
case a.TransactionType when 1 then a.Quantity when 2 then case when a.Quantity >= 0 then a.Quantity else null end else null end as InQuantity,
case a.TransactionType when 1 then a.Quantity * a.ItemCost when 2 then case a.TranTypeID when 11 then case when a.Quantity >= 0 then a.TransactionAmount else null end else case when a.Quantity >= 0 then a.Quantity * a.ItemCost else null end end else null end as InAmount,
case a.TransactionType when 0 then a.Quantity when 2 then case when a.Quantity <= 0 then ABS(a.Quantity) else null end else null end as OutQuantity,
case a.TransactionType when 0 then a.Quantity * a.ItemCost when 2 then case a.TranTypeID when 11 then case when a.Quantity <= 0 then ABS(a.Quantity) * a.ItemCost else null end else case when a.Quantity <= 0 then ABS(a.Quantity) * a.ItemCost else null end end else null end as OutAmount
FROM ( SELECT DISTINCT MST_TransactionHistory.TranTypeID, MST_TransactionHistory.LocationID, ITM_Product.ProductID, MST_MasterLocation.Code AS MasLocCode, MST_Location.Code AS LocationCode, MST_Bin.Code as BinCode, MST_TransactionHistory.PostDate, ITM_Product.Code as PartNumber, ITM_Product.Description PartName, ITM_Product.Revision PartModel, MST_UnitOfMeasure.Code AS UMCode,
MST_TranType.Description as TranTypeName, MST_TranType.Code as TranTypeCode, MST_TranType.Type as TransactionType,
(IV_BinCache.OHQuantity - ( SELECT ISNULL(SUM(TransQuantity), 0) FROM v_TransactionHistory INNER JOIN MST_TranType ON v_TransactionHistory.TranTypeID = MST_TranType.TranTypeID WHERE ProductID = IV_BinCache.ProductID AND BinID = IV_BinCache.BinID AND PostDate >= @FromDate AND (MST_TranType.Type = 1 OR MST_TranType.Type = 2) ) + ( SELECT ISNULL(SUM(TransQuantity), 0) FROM v_TransactionHistory INNER JOIN MST_TranType ON v_TransactionHistory.TranTypeID = MST_TranType.TranTypeID WHERE ProductID = IV_BinCache.ProductID AND BinID = IV_BinCache.BinID AND PostDate >= @FromDate AND MST_TranType.Type = 0 ) ) as BeginStock,
MST_TransactionHistory.Quantity,
ISNULL( ( Case When ( SELECT SUM(cost.ActualCost) FROM CST_ActualCostHistory cost INNER JOIN cst_ActCostAllocationMaster cycle ON cycle.ActCostAllocationMasterID = cost.ActCostAllocationMasterID WHERE cost.ProductID = ITM_Product.ProductID AND (DATEADD(day, -1, @FromDate) BETWEEN cycle.FromDate AND cycle.FromDate) ) Is Not Null Then (SELECT SUM(cost.ActualCost) FROM CST_ActualCostHistory cost INNER JOIN cst_ActCostAllocationMaster cycle ON cycle.ActCostAllocationMasterID = cost.ActCostAllocationMasterID WHERE cost.ProductID = ITM_Product.ProductID AND (DATEADD(day, -1, @FromDate) BETWEEN cycle.FromDate AND cycle.FromDate) ) Else (SELECT SUM(Cost) FROM CST_STDItemCost WHERE ProductID = ITM_Product.ProductID) End) , 0) as BeginItemCost,
-- Get item cost based on @ToDate ISNULL( ( Case When ( SELECT SUM(cost.ActualCost) FROM CST_ActualCostHistory cost INNER JOIN cst_ActCostAllocationMaster cycle ON cycle.ActCostAllocationMasterID = cost.ActCostAllocationMasterID WHERE cost.ProductID = ITM_Product.ProductID AND (@ToDate BETWEEN cycle.FromDate AND cycle.FromDate) ) Is Not Null Then (SELECT SUM(cost.ActualCost) FROM CST_ActualCostHistory cost INNER JOIN cst_ActCostAllocationMaster cycle ON cycle.ActCostAllocationMasterID = cost.ActCostAllocationMasterID WHERE cost.ProductID = ITM_Product.ProductID AND (@ToDate BETWEEN cycle.FromDate AND cycle.FromDate) ) Else (SELECT SUM(Cost) FROM CST_STDItemCost WHERE ProductID = ITM_Product.ProductID) End) , 0) as StockItemCost,
ISNULL( ( Case When ( SELECT SUM(cost.ActualCost) FROM CST_ActualCostHistory cost INNER JOIN cst_ActCostAllocationMaster cycle ON cycle.ActCostAllocationMasterID = cost.ActCostAllocationMasterID WHERE cost.ProductID = ITM_Product.ProductID AND (MST_TransactionHistory.PostDate BETWEEN cycle.FromDate AND cycle.FromDate)
) Is Not Null Then (SELECT SUM(cost.ActualCost) FROM CST_ActualCostHistory cost INNER JOIN cst_ActCostAllocationMaster cycle ON cycle.ActCostAllocationMasterID = cost.ActCostAllocationMasterID WHERE cost.ProductID = ITM_Product.ProductID AND (MST_TransactionHistory.PostDate BETWEEN cycle.FromDate AND cycle.FromDate) ) Else (SELECT SUM(Cost) FROM CST_STDItemCost WHERE ProductID = ITM_Product.ProductID) End) , 0) as ItemCost,
case MST_TranType.Code -- 11: PO Receipt when 'POPurchaseOrderReceipts' then -- Receipt by PO Case when (SELECT InvoiceMasterID FROM PO_PurchaseOrderReceiptMaster WHERE PurchaseOrderReceiptID = MST_TransactionHistory.RefMasterID) is null then ( ( SELECT ISNULL(po.ExchangeRate, 1) * poi.UnitPrice * ABS(MST_TransactionHistory.Quantity)
FROM PO_PurchaseOrderDetail poi INNER JOIN PO_PurchaseOrderMaster po ON po.PurchaseOrderMasterID = poi.PurchaseOrderMasterID INNER JOIN PO_PurchaseOrderReceiptMaster prm ON prm.PurchaseOrderMasterID = po.PurchaseOrderMasterID INNER JOIN PO_PurchaseOrderReceiptDetail prd ON prd.PurchaseOrderDetailID = poi.PurchaseOrderDetailID AND prd.PurchaseOrderReceiptID = prm.PurchaseOrderReceiptID
WHERE prm.PurchaseOrderReceiptID = MST_TransactionHistory.RefMasterID AND prd.PurchaseOrderReceiptDetailID = MST_TransactionHistory.RefDetailID )
+ ( SELECT ISNULL(SUM(cst_FreightDetail.Amount * cst_FreightMaster.ExchangeRate), 0) FROM PO_PurchaseOrderReceiptMaster INNER JOIN cst_FreightMaster ON cst_FreightMaster.PurchaseOrderReceiptID = PO_PurchaseOrderReceiptMaster.PurchaseOrderReceiptID INNER JOIN cst_FreightDetail ON cst_FreightDetail.FreightMasterID = cst_FreightMaster.FreightMasterID WHERE PO_PurchaseOrderReceiptMaster.PurchaseOrderReceiptID = MST_TransactionHistory.RefMasterID AND cst_FreightDetail.ProductID = ITM_Product.ProductID AND cst_FreightMaster.ACPurposeID = 3 -- Credit ) -
( SELECT ISNULL(SUM(cst_FreightDetail.Amount * cst_FreightMaster.ExchangeRate), 0) FROM PO_PurchaseOrderReceiptMaster INNER JOIN cst_FreightMaster ON cst_FreightMaster.PurchaseOrderReceiptID = PO_PurchaseOrderReceiptMaster.PurchaseOrderReceiptID INNER JOIN cst_FreightDetail ON cst_FreightDetail.FreightMasterID = cst_FreightMaster.FreightMasterID WHERE PO_PurchaseOrderReceiptMaster.PurchaseOrderReceiptID = MST_TransactionHistory.RefMasterID AND cst_FreightDetail.ProductID = ITM_Product.ProductID AND cst_FreightMaster.ACPurposeID = 4 -- Debit ) ) -- Receipt by invoice else ( SELECT TOP 1 (ISNULL(inv.ExchangeRate, 1) * invd.UnitPrice * ABS(MST_TransactionHistory.Quantity)) + ISNULL(inv.ExchangeRate, 1) * invd.Inland + ISNULL(inv.ExchangeRate, 1) * invd.ImportTaxAmount
FROM PO_InvoiceDetail invd INNER JOIN dbo.PO_InvoiceMaster inv ON inv.InvoiceMasterID = invd.InvoiceMasterID INNER JOIN PO_PurchaseOrderReceiptMaster prm ON prm.InvoiceMasterID = inv.InvoiceMasterID INNER JOIN PO_PurchaseOrderReceiptDetail prd ON prd.PurchaseOrderDetailID = invd.PurchaseOrderDetailID AND prd.PurchaseOrderReceiptID = prm.PurchaseOrderReceiptID
WHERE prm.PurchaseOrderReceiptID = MST_TransactionHistory.RefMasterID AND prd.PurchaseOrderReceiptDetailID = MST_TransactionHistory.RefDetailID )
+ ( SELECT ISNULL(SUM(cst_FreightDetail.Amount * cst_FreightMaster.ExchangeRate), 0) FROM PO_PurchaseOrderReceiptMaster INNER JOIN cst_FreightMaster ON cst_FreightMaster.PurchaseOrderReceiptID = PO_PurchaseOrderReceiptMaster.PurchaseOrderReceiptID INNER JOIN cst_FreightDetail ON cst_FreightDetail.FreightMasterID = cst_FreightMaster.FreightMasterID WHERE PO_PurchaseOrderReceiptMaster.PurchaseOrderReceiptID = MST_TransactionHistory.RefMasterID AND cst_FreightDetail.ProductID = ITM_Product.ProductID AND cst_FreightMaster.ACPurposeID <> 3 -- Credit, Freight, Import Tax )
-
( SELECT ISNULL(SUM(cst_FreightDetail.Amount * cst_FreightMaster.ExchangeRate), 0) FROM PO_PurchaseOrderReceiptMaster INNER JOIN cst_FreightMaster ON cst_FreightMaster.PurchaseOrderReceiptID = PO_PurchaseOrderReceiptMaster.PurchaseOrderReceiptID INNER JOIN cst_FreightDetail ON cst_FreightDetail.FreightMasterID = cst_FreightMaster.FreightMasterID WHERE PO_PurchaseOrderReceiptMaster.PurchaseOrderReceiptID = MST_TransactionHistory.RefMasterID AND cst_FreightDetail.ProductID = ITM_Product.ProductID AND cst_FreightMaster.ACPurposeID = 4 -- Debit )
end End as TransactionAmount,
case MST_TranType.Code -- SOReturnGoodsReceive When 'SOReturnGoodsReceive' then (Select ReturnedGoodsNumber From SO_ReturnedGoodsMaster Where ReturnedGoodsMasterID = MST_TransactionHistory.RefMasterID )
-- SOCancelCommitment When 'SOCancelCommitment' then (Select CommitmentNo From SO_CommitInventoryMaster Where CommitInventoryMasterID = MST_TransactionHistory.RefMasterID )
-- PO_PurchaseOrderReceiptMaster when 'PO_PurchaseOrderReceiptMaster' then (SELECT ReceiveNo FROM PO_PurchaseOrderReceiptMaster WHERE PO_PurchaseOrderReceiptMaster.PurchaseOrderReceiptID = MST_TransactionHistory.RefMasterID )
--12 POReturnToVendor When 'POReturnToVendor' then (Select RTVNo From PO_ReturnToVendorMaster Where ReturnToVendorMasterID = MST_TransactionHistory.RefMasterID )
--13 IVMaterialReceipt when 'IVMaterialReceipt' then (Select TransNo From dbo.IV_MaterialReceipt Where MaterialReceiptID = MST_TransactionHistory.RefMasterID )
--14 IVMaterialIssue when 'IVMaterialIssue' then (Select TransNo From dbo.IV_MaterialIssue Where MaterialIssueMasterID = MST_TransactionHistory.RefMasterID )
--17 IVInventoryAdjustment when 'IVInventoryAdjustment' then (Select TransNo From dbo.IV_Adjustment Where AdjustmentID = MST_TransactionHistory.RefMasterID )
--19 PROWorkOrderCompletion when 'PROWorkOrderCompletion' then (Select WOCompletionNo From dbo.PRO_WorkOrderCompletion Where WorkOrderCompletionID = MST_TransactionHistory.RefMasterID )
--21 PROIssueMaterial when 'PROIssueMaterial' then (Select IssueNo From dbo.PRO_IssueMaterialMaster Where IssueMaterialMasterID = MST_TransactionHistory.RefMasterID )
--22 ShippingManagement when 'ShippingManagement' then (Select ConfirmShipNo From dbo.SO_ConfirmShipMaster Where ConfirmShipMasterID = MST_TransactionHistory.RefMasterID )
--23 SOCommitment when 'SOCommitment' then (Select CommitmentNo From dbo.SO_CommitInventoryMaster Where CommitInventoryMasterID = MST_TransactionHistory.RefMasterID )
--24 IVMiscellaneousIssue when 'IVMiscellaneousIssue' then (Select TransNo From dbo.IV_MiscellaneousIssueMaster Where MiscellaneousIssueMasterID = MST_TransactionHistory.RefMasterID )
--25 RecoverableMaterial when 'RecoverableMaterial' then (Select TransNo From dbo.CST_RecoverMaterialMaster Where RecoverMaterialMasterID = MST_TransactionHistory.RefMasterID )
--26 ShippingAdjustment when 'ShippingAdjustment' then (Select ConfirmShipNo From dbo.SO_ConfirmShipMaster Where ConfirmShipMasterID = MST_TransactionHistory.RefMasterID )
End as TransactionNo,
case MST_TransactionHistory.TranTypeID --21 PROIssueMaterial when 21 then Case -- Get From location Code when MST_TransactionHistory.Quantity >= 0 then (SELECT Code FROM MST_Location loc INNER JOIN PRO_IssueMaterialDetail ON PRO_IssueMaterialDetail.LocationID = loc.LocationID WHERE PRO_IssueMaterialDetail.IssueMaterialDetailID = MST_TransactionHistory.RefDetailID ) Else -- Get To location Code (SELECT Code FROM MST_Location loc INNER JOIN PRO_IssueMaterialMaster ON PRO_IssueMaterialMaster.ToLocationID = loc.LocationID WHERE PRO_IssueMaterialMaster.IssueMaterialMasterID = MST_TransactionHistory.RefMasterID ) End
--24 IVMiscellaneousIssue when 24 then Case -- Get From location Code when MST_TransactionHistory.Quantity >= 0 then (SELECT Code FROM MST_Location loc INNER JOIN IV_MiscellaneousIssueMaster ON IV_MiscellaneousIssueMaster.SourceLocationID = loc.LocationID WHERE IV_MiscellaneousIssueMaster.MiscellaneousIssueMasterID = MST_TransactionHistory.RefMasterID ) Else -- Get To location Code (SELECT Code FROM MST_Location loc INNER JOIN IV_MiscellaneousIssueMaster ON IV_MiscellaneousIssueMaster.DesLocationID = loc.LocationID WHERE IV_MiscellaneousIssueMaster.MiscellaneousIssueMasterID = MST_TransactionHistory.RefMasterID ) End
--25 RecoverableMaterial when 25 then Case -- Get From location Code when MST_TransactionHistory.Quantity >= 0 then (SELECT Code FROM MST_Location loc INNER JOIN CST_RecoverMaterialMaster ON CST_RecoverMaterialMaster.FromLocationID = loc.LocationID WHERE CST_RecoverMaterialMaster.RecoverMaterialMasterID = MST_TransactionHistory.RefMasterID ) Else '' End Else '' End as RelatedLocation,
case MST_TransactionHistory.TranTypeID --21 PROIssueMaterial when 21 then Case -- Get From location Code when MST_TransactionHistory.Quantity >= 0 then (SELECT Code FROM MST_Bin bin INNER JOIN PRO_IssueMaterialDetail ON PRO_IssueMaterialDetail.BinID = bin.BinID WHERE PRO_IssueMaterialDetail.IssueMaterialDetailID = MST_TransactionHistory.RefDetailID ) Else -- Get To location Code (SELECT Code FROM MST_Bin bin INNER JOIN PRO_IssueMaterialMaster ON PRO_IssueMaterialMaster.ToBinID = bin.BinID WHERE PRO_IssueMaterialMaster.IssueMaterialMasterID = MST_TransactionHistory.RefMasterID ) End
--24 IVMiscellaneousIssue when 24 then Case -- Get From location Code when MST_TransactionHistory.Quantity >= 0 then (SELECT Code FROM MST_Bin bin INNER JOIN IV_MiscellaneousIssueMaster ON IV_MiscellaneousIssueMaster.SourceBinID = bin.BinID WHERE IV_MiscellaneousIssueMaster.MiscellaneousIssueMasterID = MST_TransactionHistory.RefMasterID ) Else -- Get To location Code (SELECT Code FROM MST_Bin bin INNER JOIN IV_MiscellaneousIssueMaster ON IV_MiscellaneousIssueMaster.DesBinID = bin.BinID WHERE IV_MiscellaneousIssueMaster.MiscellaneousIssueMasterID = MST_TransactionHistory.RefMasterID ) End
--25 RecoverableMaterial when 25 then Case -- Get From location Code when MST_TransactionHistory.Quantity >= 0 then (SELECT Code FROM MST_Bin bin INNER JOIN CST_RecoverMaterialMaster ON CST_RecoverMaterialMaster.FromBinID = bin.BinID WHERE CST_RecoverMaterialMaster.RecoverMaterialMasterID = MST_TransactionHistory.RefMasterID ) Else '' End Else '' End as RelatedBin
FROM MST_TransactionHistory INNER JOIN IV_BinCache ON MST_TransactionHistory.ProductID = IV_BinCache.ProductID AND MST_TransactionHistory.BinID = IV_BinCache.BinID
INNER JOIN MST_TranType ON MST_TransactionHistory.TranTypeID = MST_TranType.TranTypeID INNER JOIN MST_Location ON MST_TransactionHistory.LocationID = MST_Location.LocationID INNER JOIN MST_Bin ON MST_TransactionHistory.BinID = MST_Bin.BinID INNER JOIN MST_MasterLocation ON MST_TransactionHistory.MasterLocationID = MST_MasterLocation.MasterLocationID INNER JOIN ITM_Product ON MST_TransactionHistory.ProductID = ITM_Product.ProductID
LEFT JOIN MST_UnitOfMeasure ON MST_TransactionHistory.StockUMID = MST_UnitOfMeasure.UnitOfMeasureID
WHERE (MST_TransactionHistory.PostDate BETWEEN @FromDate AND @ToDate) AND MST_TranType.Type IN (0, 1, 2)
) a
ORDER BY a.MasLocCode, a.LocationCode, a.BinCode, a.PostDate
